These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, golf, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | volleyball | golf | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, cranberry, plum
1. the person eating cranberry is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | kiwi | plum | cranberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, writing, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | photography | writing | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, hip-hop, salsa
1. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | salsa | hip-hop |

